# 🚀 NextGen Campus — Full Deployment Guide

> **Frontend:** Vercel (React + Vite)  
> **Backend:** Render (Flask + Gunicorn)  
> **Database:** PostgreSQL (Render) / SQLite (fallback)  
> **Repository:** [github.com/pratikayalapujith/Nextgen_Campus_](https://github.com/pratikayalapujith/Nextgen_Campus_)

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
next campus/
├── .python-version          ← Pins Python 3.11 for Render
├── .gitignore
├── render.yaml              ← Render Blueprint (optional)
├── backend/
│   ├── run.py               ← Flask entry point
│   ├── requirements.txt     ← Python dependencies
│   └── app/
│       ├── __init__.py      ← App factory + auto-seed logic
│       ├── config.py         ← Dev / Prod / Test configs
│       ├── extensions.py     ← SQLAlchemy, JWT, CORS, Migrate
│       ├── models/           ← Database models (User, Student, etc.)
│       ├── routes/           ← API endpoints (auth, students, etc.)
│       ├── seeds/            ← Seed data for demo accounts
│       ├── services/         ← Business logic
│       └── utils/            ← Utilities
└── frontend/
    ├── vercel.json          ← SPA rewrite rules for Vercel
    ├── package.json         ← Node dependencies
    ├── vite.config.ts       ← Vite dev server + proxy config
    └── src/
        ├── api/axios.ts     ← Axios instance with auth interceptors
        ├── utils/constants.ts ← API_BASE URL (env-aware)
        ├── context/AuthContext.tsx ← Auth state management
        └── pages/            ← Login, Dashboard, etc.
```

