## 🌐 How the Full Flow Works

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Vercel as Vercel (Frontend)
    participant Render as Render (Backend)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Vercel: Opens https://nextgen-campus.vercel.app
    Vercel-->>User: Serves React SPA (index.html + JS)
    
    User->>Vercel: Enters email/password, clicks Login
    Note over Vercel: React reads VITE_API_URL
    Vercel->>Render: POST /api/auth/login {email, password}
    Render->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE email=?
    DB-->>Render: User record
    Render->>Render: check_password(hash, input)
    Render-->>Vercel: {access_token, refresh_token, user}
    Vercel->>Vercel: Stores tokens in localStorage
    Vercel-->>User: Redirects to Dashboard

    User->>Vercel: Clicks "Students" page
    Vercel->>Render: GET /api/students (Authorization: Bearer <token>)
    Render->>Render: JWT verification
    Render->>DB: SELECT * FROM students
    DB-->>Render: Student records
    Render-->>Vercel: [{student1}, {student2}, ...]
    Vercel-->>User: Renders student list
```

