## 🔄 API Routes Reference

All routes are prefixed with `/api`:

| Method | Route | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | No | Create new user |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | No | Login, get JWT tokens |
| POST | `/api/auth/refresh` | Refresh Token | Get new access token |
| POST | `/api/auth/logout` | Access Token | Blacklist current token |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | Access Token | Get current user profile |
| PUT | `/api/auth/me` | Access Token | Update profile |
| PUT | `/api/auth/change-password` | Access Token | Change password |
| GET/POST | `/api/students` | Access Token | List / Create students |
| GET/POST | `/api/faculty` | Access Token | List / Create faculty |
| GET/POST | `/api/departments` | Access Token | List / Create departments |
| GET/POST | `/api/subjects` | Access Token | List / Create subjects |
| GET/POST | `/api/timetable` | Access Token | List / Create timetable entries |
| GET/POST | `/api/attendance` | Access Token | List / Mark attendance |
| GET/POST | `/api/notices` | Access Token | List / Create notices |
| GET/POST | `/api/facilities` | Access Token | List / Create facilities |
| GET/POST | `/api/bookings` | Access Token | List / Create bookings |
| GET | `/api/dashboard` | Access Token | Dashboard statistics |

