## 📋 Deployment Checklist

### Backend (Render)
- [ ] Push code to GitHub
- [ ] Create Web Service on Render → connect GitHub repo
- [ ] Set **Build Command:** `cd backend && pip install -r requirements.txt`
- [ ] Set **Start Command:** `gunicorn --chdir backend run:app`
- [ ] Create PostgreSQL database on Render
- [ ] Add env var `DATABASE_URL` (Internal DB URL from PostgreSQL)
- [ ] Add env var `SECRET_KEY` (random string)
- [ ] Add env var `JWT_SECRET_KEY` (random string)
- [ ] Deploy and check logs for `✅ Test data seeded successfully!`
- [ ] Copy the backend public URL

### Frontend (Vercel)
- [ ] Import GitHub repo on Vercel
- [ ] Set **Root Directory:** `frontend`
- [ ] Set **Framework Preset:** `Vite`
- [ ] Set **Build Command:** `npm run build`
- [ ] Set **Output Directory:** `dist`
- [ ] Add env var `VITE_API_URL`: `https://your-backend.onrender.com/api`
- [ ] Deploy
- [ ] Test login with `admin@campus.com` / `admin123`
